I am using revision 11536, url: <a href="http://framework.zend.com/svn/framework/standard/trunk/library/">http://framework.zend.com/svn/framework/â€¦</a>, and the problem that I described above happens in this revision. Isn't it the latest version? Only try the example, I think that what it does is not expected behaviour.</p>

